data.description: Come be apart of Acworth where it is ever growing! Walk through the front door where you are welcomed with upgraded LVP flooring and lighting. Into a well lit open concept with the kitchen, dining, & living room area all combined for easy entataining. Kitchen comes equipped with all stainless steel appliances, quartz countertops, and updated cabinetry. Fenced in backyard perfect for entertaining the furry friends! Upstairs includes three spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms along with your hallway laundry room. This home comes with a one car garage and extended driveway as well as easy access to any additional visitor parking one may need!
